name: Predator Cybercats Exclusive - Glitched Royal Blue Argonaut
description: Argonaut has taken his special forces through a portal into a parallel universe that has glitched him at the atomic level. In this universe he is not known to be a military fighter but a royal monarch that has endured the test of time in a mighty kingdom and commands respect of all. Will he enter another portal to the unknown or remain to lead his newfound kingdom?
